WEBVTT

00:07:28.617 --> 00:07:31.632
Because I'm focusing
on what we have in common.

00:07:35.045 --> 00:07:39.497
When you can find even the smallest bit
of common ground with somebody,

00:07:39.521 --> 00:07:44.765
it allows you to understand
just the beautiful wonder

00:07:44.789 --> 00:07:46.023
and complexity

00:07:47.415 --> 00:07:49.773
and majesty of the other person.

00:07:53.583 --> 00:07:55.579
Our second strategy

00:07:55.603 --> 00:07:57.855
gives us room to (Inhales)

00:07:57.879 --> 00:07:59.029
breathe.

00:07:59.672 --> 00:08:00.822
To pause.